{"word":"μαλθακίζομαι","slug":"μαλθακίζομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>μαλθακίζομαι</b></el> <el>(μαλθᾰκίζομαι,) </el><p/><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be softened</i>, of persons, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>:— <i>to relax, give in</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/>"}]}